description: Lists the channels in the current account, and their source names.

nested_items.name: Channels
nested_items.description: The list of channels in the account.

nested_items.name: ChannelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of a channel.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the CloudTrail channel. For service-linked channels, the name is aws-service-channel/service-name/custom-suffix where service-name represents the name of the Amazon Web Services service that created the channel and custom-suffix represents the suffix created by the Amazon Web Services service.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to get the next page of results after a previous API call.
